short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add amazing Architecture views to your New Tab

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Improve your focus and get inspiration with the most impressive Architecture art from around the world.

A new search engine tab with rotating architecture images from around the world.

The new tab  embeds a search bar. Search features are provided by Microsoft Bing. No changes to your browser default search settings will be made.
